      <title>美联储古尔斯比警告关税将影响通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/fed-s-goolsbee-warns-about-inflation-impact-of-tariffs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥联邦储备银行行长奥斯坦·古尔斯比警告称，持续的关税可能导致供应链再次中断并推高通胀。他在底特律芝加哥联邦储备银行的汽车会议上发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/fed-s-goolsbee-warns-about-inflation-impact-of-tariffs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 20:37:08 GMT</pubDate>
